skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: summit guru
des: AWS Public Sector Summit 2018 includes nearly 100 partner exhibitors as well as a vast number of customer attendees. Can search for worldwide AWS public sector summit partners using voice commands in multiple ways. Can also get specific summit and AWS relationship information about specific partners attending. Information to search includes booth number, sponsor level, Amazon Partner Network status, and competencies.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
